  "keyFeatures": [
    "Knowledge graph builder that scans Python, TypeScript, Go, Rust, Java codebases into nodes and edges",
    "Graph-of-Agents reasoning: each module becomes an autonomous agent that debates and synthesizes answers",
    "27 MCP tools that plug into Claude Code, Cursor, VS Code Copilot, and Windsurf with zero config change",
    "14 LLM backends including fully offline Ollama support and smart routing by task type",
    "Impact analysis (blast radius) — which modules break if you change a given file",
    "Preflight safety checks with DRACE governance scores (5 dimensions) before making changes",
    "Persistent institutional memory: lessons survive chat resets and are surfaced automatically",
    "Phantom plugin: browser automation giving AI agents real computer skills (click, type, audit)",
    "SCORCH engine: 13-dimension UX friction auditing with Claude Vision",
    "Confidence-scored, evidence-chained answers — never just 'I think...'"
  ],
  "publicApiSurface": [
    "graq init",
    "graq scan repo <path>",
    "graq scan docs <path>",
